      * L8: 000800
      * L9: 000900 PROCEDURE DIVISION.
      * L10: 001000     ACCEPT X.
      * L11: 001100     IF (X > 100)
      * L12: 001200         MOVE X TO S.
      * L13: 001300         DISPLAY S.
      * L14: 001400     STOP RUN.
